Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.83,0:52:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Those\Nwho allege that their life is devoted to
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.35,0:53:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,God then must of necessity\Nbecome integrous. Integrous means also
