Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.52,0:53:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we're required at a point in life to\Nsay no.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.31,0:53:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's integrous to say no.\Nthe depictions of God throughout
