Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.04,0:53:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange gods, weird gods, but some kind\Nof God has existed in every society,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.83,0:53:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,what we call primitive or not. And right\Nup to this present day, the definitions
