Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.11,0:54:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The true descriptions of God have have\Nalso been attacked by those energies
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.88,0:54:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,which are really ungodly.\NDevotion to God means what? It means
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.31,0:54:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to begin with just a reverence for life.\NThe reverence for life is the awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.35,0:54:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and the acknowledgment that the essence\Nand source of all life is divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.24,0:54:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Life is God. God is life.\NTherefore, life cannot be destroyed any
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.52,0:54:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,more than God can be destroyed.\NThe proof of the existence of God is
