Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.04,0:55:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,with a little meditation or\Ncontemplation and looking at it, you
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.04,0:55:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,realize that nothing has within itself\Nthe power to create its own existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.40,0:55:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All it is\Nwould either have to come out of nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.96,0:55:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,or something.\NIf it's a golf ball,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.83,0:55:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,if it's a shirt, if it's a living,\Nbreathing human being,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.92,0:55:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't suddenly spontaneously exist out\Nof the only thing that can come into
