Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.59,0:55:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but it cannot choose to create its own\Nexistence.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.92,0:56:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No one here has the power to create his\Nown existence.
