Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.24,0:56:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a stamp of validity.\NThe presence within the knowingness of
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.64,0:57:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the being is unmistakable.\NWhy? Because it's absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.68,0:57:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When I said the\NThe power of God is so overwhelming when
