Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.96,0:57:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,absoluteness\Nor vice versa.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.40,0:57:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The absoluteness and the infinite power\Nare one and the same. It leaves an
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.83,0:57:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,unmistakable\Nimprint
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.68,0:57:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,in the aura of every single person in\Nthis room forever more.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.16,0:57:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a fact.\NThat is a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.44,0:58:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I am blessed by your presence\Nthat I may share it. [laughter]
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.20,0:58:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The pathway to salvation and the pathway\Nto enlightenment are somewhat different
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.48,0:58:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet they're the same.\NReligion
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.64,0:58:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is ordinarily practiced uh throughout\Nthe history of America has been you're
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.88,0:58:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,born into a certain religion. You go to\Nchurch. You do the best you can to
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.79,0:58:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,adhere to it.\NYou try to undo your sins. You pray. You
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.40,0:58:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you do the best you can. And you know\Nthe prognosis spiritually is very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.48,0:58:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fact.\Nto just be an ordinary god-fearing
