Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.64,0:59:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,salvation.\NIt's all that's necessary for salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.35,0:59:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't have to become a saint. You don't\Nhave to become an enlightened mystic.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.20,0:59:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to become a Buddha.\Nas long as it doesn't become oppressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.11,0:59:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And what happened with me is it became\Noppressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.11,0:59:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore I shuck the whole thing.\NAnd when I was an atheist, from the time
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.31,0:59:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I rejected God as the source of all evil\Nthat I could see until the moment of
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.44,0:59:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that stunning awareness\Nmany years later, which was like
