Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.92,1:01:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, what is witnessed is\Nunmistakable.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.35,1:01:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's unmistakable, it never\Nvaries over the course of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.68,1:01:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No mystic ever lied.\NYou pick up the radiance of the truth in
