Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.31,1:01:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The karma of lying from that level would\Nbe so dreadful and to be beyond
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.04,1:01:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,description. The thing that always\Nsurprises me about
