Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.35,1:02:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,To understand the nature of God would be\Nto be aware
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.00,1:02:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of the absoluteness of the karmic\Ncoherence of all of creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.64,1:02:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you don't have to worry about\Njudgment day
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.76,1:02:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,because judgment day is every day.\NJudgment day is right now. Judgment day
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.40,1:02:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is continuous.\NJudgment day, we have permission to ask
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.40,1:02:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,this in front of this audience. This\Njudgment day is this instant
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.00,1:02:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and this instant.\NAnd in this instant forever
